ng business because we got tired of watching good people like you get overcharged for cookie-cutter products and services.<br /><br />We give our clients our mobile phone numbers because we feel strongly that a brand is only as good as the people behind it.<br /><br />Together, we have achieved results for law firms, business publications, insurance companies, web hosting providers and many more. Let\'s talk.\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_title\";s:16:\"Content Strategy\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_text\";s:57:\"We\'re both solid copywriters who refuse to reuse content.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_nr\";s:3:\"100\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_title\";s:26:\"Search Engine Optimization\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_text\";s:66:\"Our approach to search engine optimization is simple but powerful.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_nr\";s:3:\"100\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_title\";s:14:\"Graphic Design\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_text\";s:78:\"Brian knows his way around Photoshop, and knows who to call when we need help.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_nr\";s:2:\"50\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_title\";s:7:\"Geekery\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_text\";s:86:\"Joe speaks fluent geek, managing all things technical for the company and our clients.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_nr\";s:2:\"50\";s:22:\"zerif_ourteam_subtitle\";s:87:\"The number of titles per employee is inversely proportional to the number of employees.\";s:23:\"zerif_testimonials_show\";s:1:\"1\";s:23:\"zerif_bottomribbon_text\";s:13:\"Already sold?\";s:30:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlabel\";s:12:\"Get in touch\";s:29:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlink\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:22:\"zerif_ribbonright_text\";s:15:\"What about now?\";s:29:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlabel\";s:10:\"Contact us\";s:28:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlink\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:21:\"zerif_contactus_title\";s:10:\"Let\'s Talk\";s:24:\"zerif_contactus_subtitle\";s:133:\"Talk isn\'t only cheap, it\'s free. We\'ll discuss your goals and how we may be able to help before we even ask for payment information.\";s:21:\"zerif_contactus_email\";s:24:\"info@advertisingbros.com\";s:21:\"zerif_latestnews_show\";s:1:\"1\";}','yes'),(118,'theme_switched','','yes'),(119,'_transient_timeout_plugin_slugs','1425568287','no'),(120,'_transient_plugin_slugs','a:13:{i:0;s:19:\"adminer/adminer.php\";i:1;s:19:\"akismet/akismet.php\";i:2;s:21:\"backwpup/backwpup.php\";i:3;s:17:\"clicky/clicky.php\";i:4;s:50:\"google-analytics-for-wordpress/googleanalytics.php\";i:5;s:9:\"hello.php\";i:6;s:19:\"jetpack/jetpack.php\";i:7;s:45:\"limit-login-attempts/limit-login-attempts.php\";i:8;s:17:\"revisr/revisr.php\";i:9;s:27:\"theme-check/theme-check.php\";i:10;s:27:\"updraftplus/updraftplus.php\";i:11;s:24:\"wordpress-seo/wp-seo.php\";i:12;s:27:\"wp-super-cache/wp-cache.php\";}','no'),(121,'clicky','a:7:{s:7:\"site_id\";s:9:\"100821734\";s:8:\"site_key\";s:16:\"a606a2d385af43b1\";s:14:\"admin_site_key\";s:32:\"814d16aa39a8f0250515360f44c733ce\";s:16:\"outbound_pattern\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"ignore_admin\";b:1;s:11:\"track_names\";b:1;s:15:\"cookies_disable\";b:0;}','yes'),(122,'yst_ga','a:1:{s:10:\"ga_general\";a:27:{s:10:\"ga_general\";a:23:{s:17:\"analytics_profile\";N;s:22:\"analytics_profile_code\";N;s:14:\"manual_ua_code\";i:0;s:20:\"manual_ua_code_field\";N;s:26:\"track_internal_as_outbound\";N;s:23:\"track_internal_as_label\";N;s:14:\"track_outbound\";i:0;s:14:\"anonymous_data\";i:0;s:16:\"enable_universal\";i:1;s:12:\"demographics\";i:0;s:12:\"ignore_users\";a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"editor\";}s:19:\"dashboards_disabled\";i:0;s:13:\"anonymize_ips\";i:0;s:17:\"track_download_as\";s:5:\"event\";s:19:\"extensions_of_files\";s:30:\"doc,exe,js,pdf,ppt,tgz,zip,xls\";s:14:\"track_full_url\";s:6:\"domain\";s:18:\"subdomain_tracking\";N;s:16:\"tag_links_in_rss\";i:0;s:12:\"allow_anchor\";i:0;s:16:\"add_allow_linker\";i:0;s:25:\"enhanced_link_attribution\";i:0;s:11:\"custom_code\";N;s:10:\"debug_mode\";i:0;}s:19:\"dashboards_disabled\";i:0;s