/wordpress.org/themes/cw-magazine\";s:11:\"description\";s:231:\"CW Magazine is a easily customizable Free News / Magazine WordPress Theme with numerous magazine / news related theme options and a beautiful newspaper design.Official support forum (https://themeisle.com/forums/forum/cw-magazine).\";}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:4:\"name\";s:18:\"Constructzine Lite\";s:4:\"slug\";s:18:\"constructzine-lite\";s:6:\"author\";s:8:\"codeinwp\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.3.0\";s:11:\"preview_url\";s:39:\"http://wp-themes.com/constructzine-lite\";s:14:\"screenshot_url\";s:72:\"//ts.w.org/wp-content/themes/constructzine-lite/screenshot.png?ver=1.3.0\";s:6:\"rating\";d:100;s:11:\"num_ratings\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:47:\"https://wordpress.org/themes/constructzine-lite\";s:11:\"description\";s:713:\"Constructzine Lite is a free construction company Business WordPress Theme, responsive, high-resolution corporate theme built with construction companies / businesses in mind, featuring a pixel perfect responsive corporate design, large images, other features include optional social menu, sidebar,clean, modern and minimal responsive design footer widgets and blog / business template.Some other businesses that uses it are : translators, interior design, architec, plumber,lawyer, painter, roofing business,repairing or even it consulting ones.All options are using WordPress Theme Customizer feature so you can watch changes live! Official support forum (https://themeisle.com/forums/forum/constructzine-lite).\";}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Mooveit Lite\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"mooveit-lite\";s:6:\"author\";s:8:\"codeinwp\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.0.5\";s:11:\"preview_url\";s:33:\"http://wp-themes.com/mooveit-lite\";s:14:\"screenshot_url\";s:66:\"//ts.w.org/wp-content/themes/mooveit-lite/screenshot.png?ver=1.0.5\";s:6:\"rating\";i:0;s:11:\"num_ratings\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:41:\"https://wordpress.org/themes/mooveit-lite\";s:11:\"description\";s:330:\"Mooveit Lite is free moving company responsive WordPress theme, but can be best used also for a professional lawyer business, business / corporate blog, medium corporation, or any small business. Mooveit is a premium responsive theme, translation ready and can be easily translated in Portuguese, French, German, Spanish, Italian,\";}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":11:{s:4:\"name\";s:11:\"Zifer Child\";s:4:\"slug\";s:11:\"zifer-child\";s:6:\"author\";s:8:\"codeinwp\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:11:\"preview_url\";s:32:\"http://wp-themes.com/zifer-child\";s:14:\"screenshot_url\";s:65:\"//ts.w.org/wp-content/themes/zifer-child/screenshot.png?ver=1.0.3\";s:6:\"rating\";i:0;s:11:\"num_ratings\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:40:\"https://wordpress.org/themes/zifer-child\";s:11:\"description\";s:164:\"The Zifer theme is a user optimized Photography WordPress Theme built with latest technologies, easy to customize. use it to create an awesome photography portoflio\";s:8:\"template\";s:10:\"zerif-lite\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:4:\"name\";s:13:\"PlumBelt Lite\";s:4:\"slug\";s:13:\"plumbelt-lite\";s:6:\"author\";s:8:\"codeinwp\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.2.5\";s:11:\"preview_url\";s:34:\"http://wp-themes.com/plumbelt-lite\";s:14:\"screenshot_url\";s:67:\"//ts.w.org/wp-content/themes/plumbelt-lite/screenshot.png?ver=1.2.5\";s:6:\"rating\";d:100;s:11:\"num_ratings\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:42:\"https://wordpress.org/themes/plumbelt-lite\";s:11:\"description\";s:493:\"PlumBelt is a free plumbing WordPress theme, can be used for any plumber, lawyer, dentist, acupuncturist, cleaning, moving, paiting,housecleaning, furniture, teaching company or other small business.Some of the major features of PlumBelt are responsive layout, featured images, custom menu, sticky posts and custom contact form. Theme is super clean corporate and fully responsive design suitable for a local business. Official support forum (https://themeisle.com/forums/forum/plumbelt-lite).\";}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:4:\"name\";s:1