cts and services.<br /><br />We give our clients our mobile phone numbers because we feel strongly that a brand is only as good as the people behind it.<br /><br />Together, we have achieved results for law firms, business publications, insurance companies, web hosting providers and many more. Let\'s talk.\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_title\";s:16:\"Content Strategy\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_text\";s:57:\"We\'re both solid copywriters who refuse to reuse content.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_nr\";s:3:\"100\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_title\";s:26:\"Search Engine Optimization\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_text\";s:66:\"Our approach to search engine optimization is simple but powerful.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_nr\";s:3:\"100\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_title\";s:14:\"Graphic Design\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_text\";s:78:\"Brian knows his way around Photoshop, and knows who to call when we need help.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_nr\";s:2:\"50\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_title\";s:7:\"Geekery\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_text\";s:86:\"Joe speaks fluent geek, managing all things technical for the company and our clients.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_nr\";s:2:\"50\";s:22:\"zerif_ourteam_subtitle\";s:87:\"The number of titles per employee is inversely proportional to the number of employees.\";s:23:\"zerif_testimonials_show\";b:1;s:23:\"zerif_bottomribbon_text\";s:13:\"Already sold?\";s:30:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlabel\";s:12:\"Get in touch\";s:29:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlink\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:22:\"zerif_ribbonright_text\";s:15:\"What about now?\";s:29:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlabel\";s:10:\"Contact us\";s:28:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlink\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:21:\"zerif_contactus_title\";s:10:\"Let\'s Talk\";s:24:\"zerif_contactus_subtitle\";s:133:\"Talk isn\'t only cheap, it\'s free. We\'ll discuss your goals and how we may be able to help before we even ask for payment information.\";s:20:\"zerif_googlemap_show\";b:0;s:23:\"zerif_googlemap_address\";s:16:\"Mount Laurel, NJ\";s:22:\"zerif_googlemap_static\";b:1;s:22:\"zerif_latest_news_show\";b:0;s:10:\"zerif_logo\";s:92:\"http://advertisingbrothers.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/AB-HORZ-Logo-SM-site-optimized.png\";s:23:\"zerif_ourfocus_subtitle\";s:33:\"Here are the things that drive us\";s:28:\"zerif_bigtitle_redbutton_url\";s:6:\"#focus\";s:20:\"zerif_ourfocus_title\";s:30:\"<a name=\"focus\"></a> Our Focus\";s:21:\"zerif_socials_twitter\";s:38:\"http://twitter.com/advertisingbrothers\";s:22:\"zerif_socials_linkedin\";s:40:\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/4857355\";s:24:\"zerif_socials_googleplus\";s:51:\"https://plus.google.com/113818592337118382038/about\";s:16:\"background_image\";s:81:\"http://advertisingbrothers.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/SMALLER-HD-IMG_0678.jpg\";s:17:\"background_repeat\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:21:\"background_position_x\";s:6:\"center\";s:21:\"background_attachment\";s:5:\"fixed\";s:25:\"zerif_bigtitle_background\";s:16:\"rgba(0,0,0,0.01)\";s:21:\"zerif_contactus_email\";s:24:\"info@advertisingbros.com\";s:23:\"zerif_contactus_sitekey\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"zerif_email\";s:28:\"info@advertisingbrothers.com\";s:11:\"zerif_phone\";s:12:\"215-253-7146\";s:13:\"zerif_address\";s:16:\"Mount Laurel, NJ\";}','yes'),(274,'safecss_revision_migrated','1425304116','yes'),(275,'safecss_preview_rev','4','yes'),(277,'widget_ctup-ads-widget','a:4:{i:2;a:4:{s:4:\"text\";s:112:\"Some of our competitors focus on speed, maximizing their income-per-hour. We focus on getting you what you want.\";s:4:\"link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"Your Goals\";s:9:\"image_uri\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:4:{s:4:\"text\";s:136:\"We learn how you approach your work. That way, we can maintain your personality, the soul of what makes your customers keep coming back.\";s:4:\"link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:21:\"Learning How You Work\";s:9:\"image_uri\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:4:{s:4:\"text\";s:101:\"Great design is invisible. We want to facilitate, not int